# SpritesheetAnimation.Frames property

Gets a read-only collection of the [`SpritesheetFrame`](../SpritesheetFrame.md) elements that make up this animation. The order of the frames is from start to the end of the animation.

public ReadOnlyCollection<SpritesheetFrame> Frames { get; }
